      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WHAT'S THE STORY (3) has a strong record this trip with three wins and three placings from nine starts. Comes off a (22.76) win last time, scoring by 2 lengths in a Grade 5 over 400m at this track. Has the ability and should feature. BLAZING PRINCE (4) jumped from box 3 last time and ran away with an impressive win scoring by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 34.71. Has the squeeze box to overcome and will need the breaks early. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Leading chance again. MONEY PIT (5) jumped favourite and quickly to the front but run down late to finish third (23.12) at this track in a Grade 5 over 400m. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Expected to be in this for a long way. KALANI SEA (8) hit the frame here last start so don't underestimate.",
